{"id":1391,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":93,"title":"93. Where is the post office","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":10,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/93-where-is-the-post-office.1391/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/0-conversation-where-is-the-post-office.mp3","transcript":"Excuse me. I'm trying to find the nearest post office.\nCan you help me?\nSure. It's not far from here.\nJust go straight down this road for about three blocks.\nYou'll see a bakery on your right.\nThe post office is right next to it,\nyou can't miss it.\nThank you! Do you know what time it closes?\nI think it closes at 5 PM.\nYou should have plenty of time if you go now.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:09","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Excuse me. I'm trying to find the nearest post office.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/1.mp3","time_start":0.41,"time_end":4.04},{"position":2,"content":"Can you help me?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/2.mp3","time_start":4.04,"time_end":5.05},{"position":3,"content":"Sure. It's not far from here.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/3.mp3","time_start":5.05,"time_end":7.75},{"position":4,"content":"Just go straight down this road for about three blocks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/4.mp3","time_start":7.75,"time_end":11.37},{"position":5,"content":"You'll see a bakery on your right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/5.mp3","time_start":11.37,"time_end":13.69},{"position":6,"content":"The post office is right next to it,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/6.mp3","time_start":13.69,"time_end":15.91},{"position":7,"content":"you can't miss it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/7.mp3","time_start":15.91,"time_end":17.15},{"position":8,"content":"Thank you! Do you know what time it closes?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/8.mp3","time_start":17.39,"time_end":20.16},{"position":9,"content":"I think it closes at 5 PM.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/9.mp3","time_start":20.16,"time_end":22.68},{"position":10,"content":"You should have plenty of time if you go now.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-where-is-the-post-office-2024-07-21-17-19-00/10.mp3","time_start":22.68,"time_end":25.52}]}